    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously cared for and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory and a complete, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
