    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of excellence. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to quality. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unparalleled ownership opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
